=Description=

"The NextFab Organization exists to promote the advancement and accessibility of the technology known as "personal fabrication". The NextFab Organization has grown out of the Fab@Home project. Fab@Home is a project dedicated to making and using fabbers - machines that can make almost anything, right on your desktop. This blog intent is to show all development done by the NextFab Organization to improve the initial design of fab@home machine."



